WEBVTT

00:11:25.263 --> 00:11:30.097
This is to show you
that this method works.

00:11:30.097 --> 00:11:34.663
And in some cases, in Cuba,
Mexico and India,

00:11:34.663 --> 00:11:37.963
the dose can be reduced to 25 percent,
and in several other cases,

00:11:37.963 --> 00:11:40.097
there's no need to add
any phosphorus at all,

00:11:40.097 --> 00:11:42.563
because the mushrooms are so well adapted

00:11:42.563 --> 00:11:45.297
to finding phosphorus
and drawing it from the soil.

00:11:45.763 --> 00:11:50.263
This is an example of soy production
in Canada.

00:11:51.597 --> 00:11:58.563
Mycorrhiza was used in one field
but not in the other.

00:11:58.763 --> 00:12:05.763
And here, where blue
indicates a better yield,